data.title: Barry Davis
data.meta_description: Barry Davis. Director: J. Robert Oppenheimer - Atomphysiker. Barry Davis was born on 11 April 1936. He was a director and writer, known for J. Robert Oppenheimer - Atomphysiker (1980), Telford's Change (1979) and American Playhouse (1980). He was married to Brenda Fricker. He died on 15 September 1990 in Llantrisant, Rhondda Cynon Taff, Wales, UK.
data.text: Barry Davis was born on April 11, 1936. He was a director and writer, known for J. Robert Oppenheimer - Atomphysiker (1980), Telford's Change (1979) and American Playhouse (1980).
